ansible
=======
# use the inventory file in your current directory 
# default inventory shoud be /etc/ansible/hosts
$ ansible -i inventory 

#test if the remote server is accessible
# make sure that the remote server has been added
# to the inventory file
# :q

$ ansible all -i invnetory -m ping
